=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides information about the phrases blocked from chat by your chat
control configuration.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 BlockedPhrases => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

A list of phrases blocked from a Amazon Q Business web experience chat.


=head2 SystemMessageOverride => Str

The configured custom message displayed to an end user informing them
that they've used a blocked phrase during chat.



